ramapurada ravana ( kannada : ರಾಮಾಪುರದ ರಾವಣ ) is a 1984 indian kannada film , directed by rajachandra and produced by c jayaram and g radhakrishna . the film stars anant nag , geetha , aarathi and thoogudeepa srinivas in lead roles . the film had musical score by rajan-nagendra . the film was remade in tamil as naam iruvar .